ActCoastal Fisheries Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Coastal Fisheries Protection Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the COASTAL FISHERIES PROTECTION REGULATIONS in order to implement the statutory to enable Canada's ratification of the Agreement on Port State Measures to Prevent, Deter and Eliminate Illegal, Unreported and Unregulated Fishing, and support the development of a strong international regime to combat illegal, unreported and unregulated fishing.
